channel.description:
I've been testing out Summoning on the Cheezscape v. 80 release and I was wondering where to find the code for adding in things into the music tab. Such as the "Green=Unlocked", where do I find the code so that I can edit it. Flame me if you want but I'm in need of help.
thanks -dave[br][size=1]Posted at: September 06, 2006, 01:10:07 PM[/size][hr]i found out how to change the parts to for what is says for summoning, but havent figured out how to change the part that says "Green=Unlocked"
